version_description: Add multiple parameters at once. Hitting that purple button now takes you to a new page where you can add several parameters in an instant. You can customize the list of most frequently logged parameters here.
Explore page will now show much more interesting photos in a more visually appealing way.
Added ability to search aquariums.
Bug fixes and performance optimizations
Featuring icons instead of text. Redesigned and improved Account screen.
Updated charts, ability to set high/low ranges for parameters, reminder badge and many bug fixes. Happy Thanksgiving, eh.
Improved navigation, better out of bounds representation for measurements, configurable charts.
Reminder can now be renewed at regular intervals or upon completion. You can also choose not to renew a reminder.
Water changes now feature charts. Bug fixes and performance improvements.

Happy New Year! AquaticLog wishes you best aquarium keeping experience with the best app for it.
Lots of bug fixes and performance improvements in this release.
View measurements right next to charts. Edit and add new measurements from the chart view.
Better way to view aquarium photos. Bug fixes when adding measurements.
You can now send direct messages and upload product photos.
Bug fixes and performance improvements.
Added multi-line comments to measurements. Charts will show time since last measurement. Bug fixes and performance improvements.
Mark your aquariums as private. Faster way to enter measurements. Cleaner interface. Last parameter values at a glance.
Bug fixes, simplification.

AquaticLog blog is now integrated with the app, you can stay informed of any new releases and features coming as well as provide your feedback, all via the AquaticBlog tab.
Also fixes a bug when the app would crash if you click on your avatar (nobody likes that).
AquaticLog is now iOS 13 compatible. With Dark Mode support.
Bug fixes, home screen layout improvement and show totals for number of aquarium inhabitants.

Amazing update to the app. You can now see your aquarium stats, see who follows your aquarium, share your aquarium details with others, you can also move inhabitants between aquariums if you have more than one.
Happy Holidays everyone! This version brings AquaticLog to 2021 - new framework upgrade under the hood and a few significant improvements to the measurements management.
Bug fixes.
Bug fix for processing in-app purchase.
Bug fixes all around.
Bug fixes to authentication module. Better way to keep track of favourite parameters.

Maintenance and Feeding reminders are now showing up on home page.
Login bug fixes.
